<section class="howto" id="como-funciona">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <span class="sec-badge">Cómo funciona</span>
      <h2>Empieza en 3 pasos</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num dark">01</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4"/><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"/><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Descarga la App</h3>
        <p>Disponible gratis en App Store y Google Play. Instala en segundos.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num blue">02</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><line x1="8" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="8" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="3.01" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="3.01" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="3.01" y2="18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Elige tu Especialidad</h3>
        <p>Selecciona la materia y dificultad. Personaliza tu sesión de estudio.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num green">03</div>
        <div class="step-icon">
          <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>¡Aprende y Progresa!</h3>
        <p>Responde preguntas, revisa explicaciones y rastrea tu progreso en tiempo real.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
